Module com.github.robtimus.junit.support

Package com.github.robtimus.junit.support.test.io

Provides pre-defined I/O related JUnit tests.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InputStreamDelegateTests
    Base interface for testing that InputStream implementations correctly delegate to another InputStream.
    InputStreamDelegateTests.CloseTests
    Contains tests for InputStream.close().
    InputStreamTests
    Base interface for testing separate InputStream functionalities.
    InputStreamTests.AvailableTests
    Contains tests for InputStream.available().
    InputStreamTests.MarkResetTests
    Contains tests for InputStream.mark(int) and InputStream.reset().
    InputStreamTests.ReadAllBytesTests
    Contains tests for InputStream.readAllBytes().
    InputStreamTests.ReadByteTests
    Contains tests for InputStream.read().
    InputStreamTests.ReadIntoByteArrayPortionTests
    Contains tests for InputStream.read(byte[], int, int).
    InputStreamTests.ReadIntoByteArrayTests
    Contains tests for InputStream.read(byte[]).
    InputStreamTests.ReadNBytesIntoByteArrayPortionTests
    Contains tests for InputStream.readNBytes(byte[], int, int).
    InputStreamTests.ReadNBytesTests
    Contains tests for InputStream.readNBytes(int).
    InputStreamTests.SkipTests
    Contains tests for InputStream.skip(long).
    InputStreamTests.TransferToTests
    Contains tests for InputStream.transferTo(OutputStream).
    OutputStreamDelegateTests
    Base interface for testing that OutputStream implementations correctly delegate to another OutputStream.
    OutputStreamDelegateTests.CloseTests
    Contains tests for OutputStream.close().
    OutputStreamDelegateTests.FlushTests
    Contains tests for OutputStream.flush().
    OutputStreamDelegateTests.WriteByteArrayPortionTests
    Contains tests for OutputStream.write(byte[], int, int).
    OutputStreamDelegateTests.WriteByteArrayTests
    Contains tests for OutputStream.write(byte[]).
    OutputStreamDelegateTests.WriteByteTests
    Contains tests for OutputStream.write(int).
    ReaderDelegateTests
    Base interface for testing that Reader implementations correctly delegate to another Reader.
    ReaderDelegateTests.CloseTests
    Contains tests for Reader.close().
    ReaderTests
    Base interface for testing separate Reader functionalities.
    ReaderTests.MarkResetTests
    Contains tests for Reader.mark(int) and Reader.reset().
    ReaderTests.ReadCharTests
    Contains tests for Reader.read().
    ReaderTests.ReadIntoCharArrayPortionTests
    Contains tests for Reader.read(char[], int, int).
    ReaderTests.ReadIntoCharArrayTests
    Contains tests for Reader.read(char[]).
    ReaderTests.ReadIntoCharBufferTests
    Contains tests for Reader.read(CharBuffer).
    ReaderTests.ReadyTests
    Contains tests for Reader.ready().
    ReaderTests.SkipTests
    Contains tests for Reader.skip(long).
    ReaderTests.TransferToTests
    Contains tests for Reader.transferTo(Writer).
    WriterDelegateTests
    Base interface for testing that Writer implementations correctly delegate to another Writer.
    WriterDelegateTests.AppendCharSequencePortionTests
    Contains tests for Writer.append(CharSequence, int, int).
    WriterDelegateTests.AppendCharSequenceTests
    Contains tests for Writer.append(CharSequence).
    WriterDelegateTests.AppendCharTests
    Contains tests for Writer.append(char).
    WriterDelegateTests.CloseTests
    Contains tests for Writer.close().
    WriterDelegateTests.FlushTests
    Contains tests for Writer.flush().
    WriterDelegateTests.WriteCharArrayPortionTests
    Contains tests for Writer.write(char[], int, int).
    WriterDelegateTests.WriteCharArrayTests
    Contains tests for Writer.write(char[]).
    WriterDelegateTests.WriteCharTests
    Contains tests for Writer.write(int).
    WriterDelegateTests.WriteStringPortionTests
    Contains tests for Writer.write(String, int, int).
    WriterDelegateTests.WriteStringTests
    Contains tests for Writer.write(String).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    WriterDelegateTests.CharSequenceTransformationProvider
    An arguments provider for WriterDelegateTests.AppendCharSequenceTests and WriterDelegateTests.AppendCharSequencePortionTests, it returns functions to transform the test instance's content to write or long content to write into a String (identity transform), StringBuilder, StringBuffer and a generic CharSequence.
